$(ele),\n                form = $ele.parent(),\n                error = form.find('.alert');\n        error.hide();\n        form.formdisabled();\n        $ele.button(\"loading\");\n        var email = $.trim(jQuery(form).find(\".email\").val()),\n                password = $.trim(jQuery(form).find(\".password\").val()),\n                remember = $.trim(jQuery(form).find(\".remember\").val());\n        remember = (remember==\"on\"?1:0);\n        $.ajax({\n            type:\"POST\",\n            url:'https://freelancerviet.vn/dang-nhap/ajax',\n            dataType:'json',\n            data:{email:email,password:password,remember:remember},\n            success:function(data){\n                if(data.error){\n                    error.show();\n                    error.find(\"p\").html(data.error);\n                    $ele.button(\"reset\");\n                    form.formenabled();\n                }else if(data.status == \"1\"){\n//\t\t\t\t\tif(data.redirect != \"\"){\n//\t\t\t\t\t\twindow.location.href = data.redirect;\n//\t\t\t\t\t}else{\n//\t\t\t\t\t\twindow.location.reload(true);\n//\t\t\t\t\t}\n                    window.location.reload(true);\n                }else{\n                    error.show();\n                    error.find(\"p\").html(\"Có lỗi xãy ra, vui lòng thử lại\");\n                    $ele.button(\"reset\");\n                    form.formenabled();\n                }\n            },\n            error:function(){\n                error.show();\n                error.find(\"p\").html(\"Có lỗi xãy ra, vui lòng thử lại\");\n                $ele.button(\"reset\");\n                form.formenabled();\n            }\n        });\n    };\n    $(document).ready(function(){\n// Fix input element click problem\n
